subSubSection.paragraph:
Color. Individuals preserved in alcohol are whitish (
Fig. 1
). We have no information on the color patterns of living specimens.

Distribution. Barbados , Colombia and Brazil (Atlantic Ocean) (
Solís-Marín et al. 2013
). In Brazil from Amapá, Pará (Marajó Island), Maranhão, Espírito Santo (continental shelf, Banco Jaseur), Rio de Janeiro (
Oliveira et al. 2010
), and São Paulo (
Monteiro 1990
).

Depth range. From 15 to 600 m (
Borges et al. 2002
).
